    - rid: 5422255992042160440
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Good morning sir, I came from the continent because I heard that you
          have problems in the city. Who's in charge here?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160441
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Welcome to my inn! First time in Moonveil?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160442
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422255992042160443
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422255992042160444
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422255992042160445
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422255992042160446
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Someone dug up the Black Knight\u2019s grave in the old cemetery\u2026
          but the coffin was empty."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160447
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Bob, an old miner, swears something\u2019s glowing deep in the abandoned
          mine \u2014 not gold, something brighter. He hasn\u2019t been seen since"
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160448
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "The wizard across the river is looking for someone to bring him \u2018something
          living\u2026 and cursed.\u2019 Best not to ask why..."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160449
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "An innkeeper up north says something scratches at his doors every
          night\u2026 but the rooms are always empty."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160450
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Actually yes, I've never been to this part of Lunaris.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160451
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I need to ask you for a favor, obviously not for free.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160452
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Ok
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160453
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I can't leave the inn because there are too many guests. Maybe you
          could go to the warehouse to the west of the village, that big brown building.
          There are chests there with pumpkins inside. Could you bring me 8?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160454
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Yes, he robbed Rolf's field. He had beautiful corn, and the thief took
          the best. Maybe he knows something.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160455
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Ok, I will check his farm.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160456
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I would like to ask you one more thing.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160457
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Like I said before...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160458
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I need to ask you for a favor, obviously not for free.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160459
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I can't leave the inn because there are too many guests. Maybe you
          could go to the warehouse to the west of the village, that big brown building.
          There are chests there with pumpkins inside. Could you bring me 8?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160460
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: How can I help you, sir?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160461
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Go to Rolf. Maybe he knows something.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160462
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I don't need help at the moment, but ask around the village, maybe
          someone else will need it.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160463
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Do you need any help?
    - rid: 5422255992042160464
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I found an advertisement that there is a thief in the city.
    - rid: 5422255992042160465
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hey, I have pumpkins.
    - rid: 5422255992042160466
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Rolf said he saw the thief running towards the warehouse.
    - rid: 5422255992042160467
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I got rid of the bandit, he didn't want to cooperate.
    - rid: 5422255992042160468
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: See you!
    - rid: 5422255992042160469
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thank you so much!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160470
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thank you, but I don't need more pumpkins. You can keep them.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160471
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Sure, here's the key. The warehouse is in the western part of town,
          you'll definitely find it. It's a large, brown building.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160472
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thank you! I will come back soon!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160473
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Great, thank you very much. Here is a reward! '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160474
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Ok
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
